### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = <pega_tu_access_token_aqui>
@userId = <pega_el_id_del_usuario>

### ─────────────────────────────
### USERS
### ─────────────────────────────

### Listar todos los usuarios
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar usuarios paginados
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar usuarios filtrando por nombre o email (?q=)
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?q=admin
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar solo usuarios activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?active=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar solo usuarios inactivos
GET {{baseUrl}}/users?active=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Obtener usuario por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/users/one?userId={{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Activar usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "active": true
}

###

### Desactivar usuario
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{userId}}",
  "active": false
}

###
